---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services & Expertise | Jour de Chance" description="L'agence média agile pour transformer les Startups en Scale-ups. Offline & Online.">
  <Header />

  <section class="bg-slate-50 py-24 border-b border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-teal-100 text-teal-700 text-xs font-bold tracking-wide uppercase mb-6">
        Depuis 2018
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
        L'agence média qui fait passer<br>
        <span class="text-teal-500">vos campagnes à l'échelle.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-8">
        L'agilité d'une structure indépendante, la puissance d'une agence 360°.
        <br><strong>TV, Affichage, Digital :</strong> Nous activons tous les leviers pour accélérer votre croissance, sans la lourdeur des grands réseaux.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider">
        <span>• Facile</span>
        <span>• Rapide</span>
        <span>• Compétitif</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-lg shadow-gray-100 border border-gray-50 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300 relative overflow-hidden group">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity">
            <span class="text-9xl font-bold text-teal-900">1</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-teal-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-teal-600">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-7 w-7" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Stratégie & Agilité</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Fini les processus lourds des agences traditionnelles. Nous comprenons les enjeux des Startups : il faut aller vite et viser juste. Nous concevons votre plan média avec réactivité.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm font-medium text-gray-500">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="text-teal-500 text-lg">✓</span> Audit & Reco en temps record</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="text-teal-500 text-lg">✓</span> Interlocuteur unique & dédié</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="text-teal-500 text-lg">✓</span> Outils de pilotage simplifiés</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-teal-600 text-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-xl shadow-teal-200 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300 relative overflow-hidden group">
          <div class="absolute -right-10 -bottom-10 w-40 h-40 bg-teal-500 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-50"></div>

          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-white/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-white">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-7 w-7" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Activation On + Off</h3>
          <p class="text-teal-50 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Notre rareté ? Maîtriser le mix média complet. Nous brisons les silos pour créer des campagnes qui marquent les esprits partout.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm font-medium text-teal-100">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="text-white text-lg">✓</span> <strong>Offline :</strong> TV, OOH, Radio, Print</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="text-white text-lg">✓</span> <strong>Digital :</strong> Social, VOL, Display, CTV</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="text-white text-lg">✓</span> <strong>Local :</strong> SEO & Géomarketing</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-lg shadow-gray-100 border border-gray-50 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300 relative overflow-hidden group">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity">
            <span class="text-9xl font-bold text-teal-900">3</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-teal-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-teal-600">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-7 w-7" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Trading & Performance</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Accédez à la puissance d'achat des grands, avec la souplesse d'un partenaire de proximité. Nous optimisons chaque euro investi.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm font-medium text-gray-500">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="text-teal-500 text-lg">✓</span> Tarifs négociés (vs Big 5)</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="text-teal-500 text-lg">✓</span> Accès inventaires Premium</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="text-teal-500 text-lg">✓</span> Reporting transparent</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-slate-50 py-20 border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <p class="text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold text-xs mb-8">Nos terrains de jeu</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 md:gap-6">
         <span class="px-6 py-3 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm text-gray-700 font-bold border border-gray-100">📺 TV & CTV</span>
         <span class="px-6 py-3 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm text-gray-700 font-bold border border-gray-100">🏙️ OOH & DOOH</span>
         <span class="px-6 py-3 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm text-gray-700 font-bold border border-gray-100">📱 Social Ads</span>
         <span class="px-6 py-3 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm text-gray-700 font-bold border border-gray-100">🔍 Search (SEA)</span>
         <span class="px-6 py-3 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm text-gray-700 font-bold border border-gray-100">📻 Radio / Audio</span>
         <span class="px-6 py-3 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm text-gray-700 font-bold border border-gray-100">📍 SEO / GEO</span>
         <span class="px-6 py-3 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm text-gray-700 font-bold border border-gray-100">📰 Presse / Print</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-gray-900 py-20 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 to-gray-800"></div>
    
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center relative z-10">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Prêt à scaler ?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Discutons de vos objectifs de croissance. Audit rapide et premières recommandations sans engagement.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-teal-500 hover:bg-teal-600 text-white font-bold py-5 px-12 rounded-full transition-all transform hover:scale-105 shadow-xl shadow-teal-500/20 text-lg">
        Lancer mon projet
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
